    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverioDAI1"/>, p. 96, n. <citedRange>29</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.30</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>013200</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>164-167</citedRange> (date), p. <citedRange>297</citedRange>, number 37 (text)</bibl>.</p>
                    <p>For general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.
                </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <w><supplied reason="lost">ἔ</supplied>νδος</w> <w>ἀ<unclear>ν</unclear></w>
                    <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <w><supplied reason="lost">ἔλ</supplied>αιον</w> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. <supplied reason="lost">Τ</supplied>ὸ <w lemma="πᾶς">πὰ<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></w> 
                        <w lemma="ἔσειμι"><supplied reason="lost">ἐσιὸν</supplied></w> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. <w lemma="ἔξειμι"><supplied reason="lost">ἐξι</supplied>ὸ<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></w>  <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="4a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">  
            
                <p><app loc="4"><lem resp="#rosamilia2023"><supplied reason="lost">ἐξι</supplied>ὸ<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></lem>
                <rdg resp="#oliverioDAI1 #IGCyr"><supplied reason="lost">Τ</supplied>ὸ <supplied reason="lost">πὰν ἐξιὸν</supplied></rdg>
                </app></p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, sous garantie, la mesure, 
                <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; huile <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. Recette totale <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
                Dépenses <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, under guarantee, per unit, 
                <supplied reason="lost">so much</supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; oil <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. Total income <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
                Expense <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, scelta, a
                <supplied reason="lost">tanto; non scelta</supplied>; , <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; olio <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. Totale entrate <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
                Uscite <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>.[---]،مباع بعقد مسبق، للمقدار الواحد، [قيمة ما]؛ [---]؛ الزيت [---]. إجمالي الدخل [---]. النفقات[---]</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The lettering of this small fragment resembles that of <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr012200</ref> and it might be complementary with it. However the stones 
                   differ both in depth and in appearance of the back.</p>
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/></bibl> rightly points out that <foreign xml:lang="grc">τὸ πάν</foreign> is usually not repeated before <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἐξιόν</foreign>, unless 
                a detailed list of expenses is mentioned.</p>
            </div></body>
    </text>
